snippet.title: Forza Horizon 4 Ultimate Add-Ons Bundle
snippet.description: The Forza Horizon 4 Ultimate Add-Ons Bundle includes the Forza Horizon 4 Car Pass, two expansions, VIP Membership, Formula Drift Car Pack and the Best of Bond Car Pack. This add-on requires Forza Horizon 4 (game sold separately). Upgrade to Ultimate today!
